{"tid":1467901,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"懇求各位唔好割蓆","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:41:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T01:18:52.000Z","uid":88922,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"93c4dcb52963ec92555577bdf682bec3b248a9b1","tid":1467901,"uid":88922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:41:55.000Z","msg":"由6月9開始 我都好多人已經坐埋同一條船<br />\n事情都已經發生左 如果因為咁小事而割蓆 <br />\n我地隻船就注定沉 <br />\n<br />\n抗爭路好漫長 好多野大家仲要學習同成長 <br />\n今次機場單野未必乎合咁多人嘅期望 我好明白 <br />\n但始終我地未完全輸曬 我地咪諗辦法下次做好d <br />\n連登勝在人才濟濟<br />\n<br />\nBe humble 不論你咩位置嘅手足 大家都應該要有呢種態度 要願意去做得更好<br />\n<br />\n仲有 無忘初衷 緊記當初我地因為咩原因而行出黎<br />\n盡量唔好將自己變成自己所唾棄嘅人<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命 <br />\n希望有一日 大家除低口罩 gear 煲底相見互擁"},{"pid":"cc4b419886cb0ea5980101f90777abb34faf53f7","tid":1467901,"uid":88922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:46:54.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"dcf1b2ca379b602f6d89858eedf767a3f4e046aa","tid":1467901,"uid":88922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:05:54.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"1155b2ce761100ef3125ff5f984dff5d3786fdb6","tid":1467901,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:14:07.000Z","msg":"無人割"},{"pid":"460af11b679e85b1afef73d1a6d6c04194bff2d3","tid":1467901,"uid":88922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:51:03.000Z","msg":"612 721 811"},{"pid":"85c50b875391e1fffd8eb9a36d8ab79cddbbd9c6","tid":1467901,"uid":45321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:53:55.000Z","msg":"不割！！"},{"pid":"f55b989c72113c9d59403f93d6c3077d99b3bdb7","tid":1467901,"uid":193465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:57:05.000Z","msg":"本來就有一班話和理非無用既人同和理飛割左蓆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3baa9bf6cf8d660e6885fa5b241a260b0e298d89","tid":1467901,"uid":293227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:58:44.000Z","msg":"冇人割"},{"pid":"6fdc16cc02b13ecc5769f65477da398a452459ba","tid":1467901,"uid":38206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:00:01.000Z","msg":"612 721 811"},{"pid":"45d5967d015f526e3bbf8e14b4cfeeb96389cc6d","tid":1467901,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:00:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/6c057950ed65cc1fac07eb212cfe3471/tumblr_nfv4w34Uby1qcbtvqo5_250.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F6c057950ed65cc1fac07eb212cfe3471%2Ftumblr_nfv4w34Uby1qcbtvqo5_250.gif&h=74060c35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[輸出革命］由今日起，不叫港獨，改叫「廣獨」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1447204\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1447204</a><br />\n<br />\n我地係唔需要洗佢地腦，甚至唔需要接觸任何人，要做既野只需要貼去多大陸人既地方都係廣獨／粵獨poster就得....只要將廣獨思想文宣貼到通街都係，中共知道左就自然唔敢放自由行落黎<br />\n將廣獨思想輸出從而增加中共管治成本同時減少自由行黎香港！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7nZFbOE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7nZFbOE.png&h=4fd8318f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴打可以用下面條link去印，set左a5 size<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1qG8N4AsnroP--EywjjvBhkhWvLzeCzeR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D1qG8N4AsnroP--EywjjvBhkhWvLzeCzeR&d=4IYAvm%2F2ThyFbSIl4Y3Ij5KGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=953b5c67\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=1qG8N4AsnroP--EywjjvBhkhWvLzeCzeR</a>"},{"pid":"72fd971338cbbe256372901858df389d936b2f7a","tid":1467901,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:02:15.000Z","msg":"上網見好多我識既和理非都post左唔割蓆既宣言"},{"pid":"666576dc786b2f5b9a6be2987a7c37d4af0cb490","tid":1467901,"uid":258944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:08:31.000Z","msg":"818遊行 推！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmo